reviewText: I had seen this movie many years ago and had been looking for it for some time. Would have preferred a DVD copy, but this tape worked out just fine. One point...seller should have cleaned off old, sticky tape resin left around the cartridge. I had to remove it myself before placing this in my machine, where it could have done some damage.
Entertaining - certainly better than most videos being offered today.  Joely Fisher is nice to watch; but not a keeper.
The reknowned underrated actress stars searching for her sister being kidnapped by modern day pirates. It's a must see!!
